markdownRemark.html: Further on Leto's relations with the Venetian press and the commercial motives of Roman humanists in publishing in Venice, see: Piero Scapecchi, "Scrivere a mano, leggere a stampa," in Pomponio Leto e la prima Accademia Romana, ed. by Chiara Cassiani and Myriam Chiabò, Rome: Roma nel Rinascimento, 2007, pp. 41-46.
